		<scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
			<head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
			<p>Will of William Griffith, Sr., of the Indiana Territory, and indentures for land
				bought or sold in Indiana; also family Bible and other genealogical data on Griffith
				and related families, including Alkin, Barnes, Clark, Ewing, Hays, Henkle [Hinkle],
				Horback, Hungerford, Hunt, Landes, Pierce, Squires, Van Camp, and White
				families.</p>
			<p>Griffith Family. Papers, #2062. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell
				University Library.</p>
		</scopecontent>
